content: As Barney, I am proud of many things that I have accomplished throughout my life. One of my biggest accomplishments was probably the time that I managed to score tickets to the Super Bowl. It was an incredible experience and one that I'll never forget. I also consider it a major accomplishment any time I'm able to successfully "suit up" and close the deal with a beautiful woman. So, those are just a couple of examples of my many accomplishments. Is there anything else you'd like to know?
